items.title: LA fires live updates: 18 missing as death toll rises
items.description: At least 27 people are believed to be dead and more than a dozen others remain unaccounted for as multiple wildfires rage across Southern California.

items.title: LA wildfire victims: What we know about those killed
items.description: Family members have begun to identify the residents who were killed in the devastating wildfires in the Los Angeles area.

items.title: 2 dead, 2 injured after man attacks group of people with a stick
items.description: Two people are dead, and two others have been injured after a man allegedly attacked a group of homeless people with a stick, police said.
